{
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"chat 是交互式对话模式，启动后会进入 AI 工具的原生交互界面\n适合需要多轮沟通、逐步澄清、实时探索的场景\n"
,
"en"
:
"chat is an interactive conversation mode that launches the native AI tool interface\nIdeal for multi-turn communication, clarification, and real-time exploration\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"--workspace 绑定工作目录，AI 会在该目录下启动并读取 AGENTS.md\n--reference-workspace 引用外部工作空间作为只读上下文\n"
,
"en"
:
"--workspace binds a working directory; AI launches there and reads AGENTS.md\n--reference-workspace references external workspace as read-only context\n"
}
]
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent chat [options] [prompt]"
]
,
"--harness"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"指定 AI 工具（覆盖默认配置）"
,
"en"
:
"Specify AI tool (override default config)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://agent/data/harness.jso"
}
}
,
"-f|--file"
:
{
"#multiple"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"附加文件到初始提示词（可多次使用）"
,
"en"
:
"Attach file to initial prompt (can be used multiple times)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__file"
}
}
,
"--pipe"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"从管道/标准输入读取内容附加到初始提示词"
,
"en"
:
"Read content from stdin/pipe to append to initial prompt"
}
}
,
"--workspace"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"绑定工作目录，AI 在该目录下启动并读取上下文"
,
"en"
:
"Bind working directory; AI launches there and reads context"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__dir"
}
}
,
"--reference-workspace"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"引用外部工作空间作为只读上下文"
,
"en"
:
"Reference external workspace as read-only context"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__dir"
}
}
,
"--no-thinking"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"跳过 AI 思考过程，直接输出结果（节省 token）"
,
"en"
:
"Skip AI thinking process, output result directly (save tokens)"
}
}
,
"#n"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"可选的初始提示词内容，进入交互界面前发送"
,
"en"
:
"Optional initial prompt sent before entering the interactive interface"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent chat"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动交互式 AI 对话"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start interactive AI chat"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent chat --workspace ./myproject"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 在 workspace 中启动交互式对话"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start chat inside a workspace"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent chat --no-thinking"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 禁用思考模式，节省 token"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Disable thinking mode to save tokens"
}
]
}

